main_body:
The countervailing charges set out in the third column of Annex II to Regulation (EEC) No 2184/87 shall be amended as follows:
(a) in respect of currents falling within CN code 0806 20 11 or 0806 20 41 the amounts '307,52' and '194,47' are replaced by '257,31' and '144,26' respectively;
(b) in respect of dried grapes falling within CN code 0806 20 19 or 0806 20 99 the amounts '354,32' and '236,05' are replaced by '304,11' and '395,84' respectively.
